Unlock Insights and Dashboards with Field Service Intelligence

The Field Service Intelligence app provides insights from Data Cloud with CRM Analytics to identify trends across your work orders, service appointments, assets, and service resources. Access dashboards that centralize your field service data to make informed operational decisions.

Where: This feature applies to Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

Who: To use the Field Service Intelligence dashboards, you need the Field Service Intelligence User permission set. To manage the Field Service Intelligence dashboards, you need the Field Service Intelligence Admin permission set.

How: To enable Field Service Intelligence, go to Field Service Intelligence Setup in Setup, complete the required setup steps, and assign the Field Service Intelligence permission sets to users.
title: Unlocking Operational Insights with Field Service Intelligence
